               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1415" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1415" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1415" type="surname" value="KEMP"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1415" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE KEMP</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 82.) I was at Greenwich fair on the 22nd of May, between eight and nine o'clock at night—I saw the prisoner and another boy in company—I watched them for twenty minutes,</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183906170271"></xptr>
               <p>or half an hour—I saw them try several gentlemen's pockets—I then saw the prisoner go to a gentleman and lady, who were standing arm and arm together—he drew this handkerchief from the gentleman's pocket—I took the prisoner with it—I spoke to the gentleman, and he wanted the hand<lb></lb>kerchief back—I asked him his name, and he said Walbrook, London, that was all—I do not know who he was—I found another silk hand<lb></lb>kerchief on the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1416" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1416" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1416" type="surname" value="CHING"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1416" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM CHING</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 61.) I was with Kemp, and saw the prisoner and another boy—the prisoner drew this handkerchief from a gentleman's pocket—Kemp took him—I took the other boy, but he was discharged.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was only a minute at a show, when the officer took the handkerchief from the ground, and took me.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
